			<useAdviceForDataSet xml:lang="en">Use the LCI results of the raw meal grinding process to assess the environmental impact in the upstream phase of cement production. Attention should be paid to the allocation of energy and emissions between this process and subsequent processes. Ensure that the system boundaries are correctly defined, including the inputs and outputs specific to the grinding stage. Update the dataset periodically to reflect changes in the technology and practice of raw meal grinding.</useAdviceForDataSet>
			<useAdviceForDataSet xml:lang="zh">使用生料粉磨过程的生命周期清单（LCI）结果来评估水泥生产上游阶段的环境影响。应注意在此过程与后续过程之间分配能源与排放。确保正确定义系统边界，包括特定于磨碎阶段的输入与输出。定期更新数据集以反映生料粉磨技术与实践的变化。</useAdviceForDataSet>
